<!-- /Views/Tabs/Friendsм—җ нҸ¬н•ЁлҗҳлҠ” Viewsм—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©лҗҳлҠ” Styleл“Өмқ„ м •мқҳн•ҳлҠ”кіі -->
<ResourceDictionary
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:materialDesign="http://materialdesigninxaml.net/winfx/xaml/themes"
    xmlns:views="clr-namespace:ChatMessenger.Client.Views.Tabs.Friends"
    xmlns:vms="clr-namespace:ChatMessenger.Client.ViewModels.Tabs.Friends">
    <!-- мҷјмӘҪ нҢЁл„җ Style -->
    <!-- м№ңкө¬ лӘ©лЎқ н‘ңмӢң ListBox лӮҙл¶Җ Itemл“Өмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="FriendList_ListBoxItem" TargetType="ListBoxItem" BasedOn="{StaticResource MaterialDesignListBoxItem}">
        <Setter Property="Height" Value="80"/>
        <Setter Property="Padding" Value="0"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- м№ңкө¬ лӘ©лЎқ н‘ңмӢң ListBoxмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="FriendList_ListBox" TargetType="ListBox">
        <Setter Property="ItemContainerStyle" Value="{StaticResource FriendList_ListBoxItem}"/>
        <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
        <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
        <Setter Property="ScrollViewer.HorizontalScrollBarVisibility" Value="Disabled"/>
        <Setter Property="ScrollViewer.VerticalScrollBarVisibility" Value="Auto"/>
        <Setter Property="ScrollViewer.CanContentScroll" Value="True"/>
        <Setter Property="materialDesign:ScrollViewerAssist.IsAutoHideEnabled" Value="false" />
        <Setter Property="materialDesign:ListBoxAssist.IsToggle" Value="False" />
    </Style>
    <!-- Profile ListBox лӮҙл¶Җмқҳ Image, Nickname л“ұ кё°ліё м •ліҙ л°°м№ҳмҡ© Gridмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="MainShell_LeftPanel_ProfileGrid" TargetType="Grid">
        <Setter Property="Margin" Value="3"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- Profile лӮҙл¶Җмқҳ ProfileImage н‘ңмӢңмҡ© Gridмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_ProfileImageGrid" TargetType="Grid">
        <Setter Property="Width" Value="45"/>
        <Setter Property="Height" Value="45"/>
        <Setter Property="Margin" Value="10"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- ProfileImageлҘј мӣҗнҳ•мңјлЎң л§Ңл“Өм–ҙмЈјлҠ” Ellipseмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_ProfileImageEllipse" TargetType="Ellipse">
        <Setter Property="Fill" Value="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignCardBackground}"/>
        <Setter Property="Stroke" Value="{DynamicResource PrimaryHueMidBrush}"/>
        <Setter Property="StrokeThickness" Value="2"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- ProfileImage лӮҙл¶Җ кё°ліё Iconмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_ProfileImageIcon" TargetType="materialDesign:PackIcon">
        <Setter Property="Kind" Value="Account"/>
        <Setter Property="Width" Value="28"/>
        <Setter Property="Height" Value="28"/>
        <Setter Property="HorizontalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
        <Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
        <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{DynamicResource PrimaryHueMidForegroundBrush}"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- Profile лӮҙл¶Җмқҳ Nickname, StatusMessage н‘ңмӢңмҡ© StackPanelмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_InfoStackPanel" TargetType="StackPanel">
        <Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- Nickname н‘ңмӢңмҡ© TextBlockмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_InfoStackPanel_NicknameTextBlock" TargetType="TextBlock">
        <Setter Property="FontSize" Value="14"/>
        <Setter Property="FontWeight" Value="Bold"/>
        <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignBody}"/>
        <Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
    </Style>
    <!-- StatusMessage н‘ңмӢңмҡ© TextBlockмқҳ Style -->
    <Style x:Key="ProfileGrid_InfoStackPanel_StatusMessageTextBlock" TargetType="TextBlock">
        <Setter Property="FontSize" Value="13"/>
        <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignBodyLight}"/>
        <Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
        <Setter Property="TextWrapping" Value="Wrap"/>
        <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="{Binding Path=Text, RelativeSource={RelativeSource Self},
                                                         Converter={StaticResource StringToVisibilityConverter}}"/>
    </Style>
    
</ResourceDictionary>